            <div type="letter">
                <div type="text">
                    <div type="transcription">
                        <p>It will ever be a deep gratification to me to know that your Father, whom I honor from the bottom of my soul, should have heard and approved of the few words which I wrote many years ago on Slavery.<ref target="#foot.f2"/></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                
            </div>
           

            
           

            
           

